---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Privacy — Brookings View" description="What Brookings View does and doesn't collect.">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Privacy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated July 2026.</em></p>

    <p>Brookings View is a simple, static website. There are no user accounts,
    no logins, and no forms that collect personal information beyond an email
    you choose to send us.</p>

    <h2>What we collect</h2>
    <p>Our hosting provider, Cloudflare, keeps standard server logs (like IP
    address and browser type) for security and performance, in line with
    <a href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/" rel="noopener">Cloudflare's
    own privacy policy</a>. We don't run our own analytics or tracking scripts
    beyond what's disclosed on the <a href="/cookies">cookies page</a>.</p>

    <h2>If you email us</h2>
    <p>We use your email address only to respond to you. We don't add it to a
    mailing list or share it with anyone else.</p>

    <h2>Changes</h2>
    <p>If this site starts running advertising or analytics that collect more
    information, this page and the <a href="/cookies">cookies page</a> will be
    updated to reflect it before that happens.</p>

    <p>Questions? <a href="/contact">Contact us</a>.</p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
.prose { max-width: 36rem; }
.prose h2 { margin-top: 2rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
.prose p { margin: 0 0 1rem; }
</style>
